dct_title_s: Ordnance Survey of England and Wales: popular edition one-inch map. Hastings. Sheet 135
dct_description_sm: Revision 1914-19. Alternate panel title: Ordnance Survey contoured road map of Hastings. Sheet 135. Relief shown by 50 feet contour intervals and spot elevation. Surveyed in 1868-73.
